[
  {
    "channel_id": "C001GENERA",
    "reactions": ":tea:x1",
    "reply_count": "0",
    "text": "Owen got into my clinic bag before I could check it. Found the fetoscope in the dog's water bowl. Doing a full restock \u2014 might be 15 late to the staff meeting.",
    "thread_ts": "0",
    "ts": "2025-12-28T16:59:06+00:00",
    "user_id": "U001PERSONA"
  },
  {
    "channel_id": "C001GENERA",
    "reactions": ":tea:x1",
    "reply_count": "0",
    "text": "Was it the good one or the backup? Also where was Neil during all this",
    "thread_ts": "0",
    "ts": "2025-12-28T16:59:06+00:00-v2",
    "user_id": "U002DANI"
  },
  {
    "channel_id": "C001GENERA",
    "reactions": ":tea:x1",
    "reply_count": "0",
    "text": "The good one. Neil was 'making coffee.' Hazel filmed the whole thing on his phone so at least there's documentation.",
    "thread_ts": "0",
    "ts": "2025-12-28T16:59:06+00:00-v3",
    "user_id": "U001PERSONA"
  },
  {
    "channel_id": "C001GENERA",
    "reactions": ":tea:x1",
    "reply_count": "0",
    "text": "Hazel is going to be a litigator. I'll grab you coffee from the break room, you'll need it.",
    "thread_ts": "0",
    "ts": "2025-12-28T16:59:06+00:00-v4",
    "user_id": "U002DANI"
  },
  {
    "channel_id": "C001GENERA",
    "reactions": ":tea:x1",
    "reply_count": "0",
    "text": "You are genuinely keeping me functional. Leaving in 5.",
    "thread_ts": "0",
    "ts": "2025-12-28T16:59:06+00:00-v5",
    "user_id": "U001PERSONA"
  },
  {
    "channel_id": "C001GENERA",
    "reactions": ":tea:x1",
    "reply_count": "0",
    "text": "Meeting got pushed back 10 min anyway. Also I have your extra doppler gel from last Tuesday sitting on my desk.",
    "thread_ts": "0",
    "ts": "2025-12-28T16:59:06+00:00-v6",
    "user_id": "U002DANI"
  },
  {
    "channel_id": "C001GENERA",
    "reactions": ":tea:x1",
    "reply_count": "0",
    "text": "I knew something was off in that bag. Asheville traffic is doing its thing so ETA still iffy.",
    "thread_ts": "0",
    "ts": "2025-12-28T16:59:06+00:00-v7",
    "user_id": "U001PERSONA"
  },
  {
    "channel_id": "C001GENERA",
    "reactions": ":tea:x1",
    "reply_count": "0",
    "text": "I'll stall. Drive safe.",
    "thread_ts": "0",
    "ts": "2025-12-28T16:59:06+00:00-v8",
    "user_id": "U002DANI"
  },
  {
    "channel_id": "C001GENERA",
    "reactions": ":tea:x1",
    "reply_count": "0",
    "text": "Hazel got into my clinic bag last night. Fetoscope is missing. I've checked under every couch cushion.",
    "thread_ts": "0",
    "ts": "2025-12-28T22:32:42+00:00",
    "user_id": "U001PERSONA"
  },
  {
    "channel_id": "C001GENERA",
    "reactions": ":tea:x1",
    "reply_count": "0",
    "text": "oh no. did you try her toy kitchen? she hid my phone in the plastic pot once lol",
    "thread_ts": "0",
    "ts": "2025-12-28T22:32:42+00:00-v2",
    "user_id": "U003THERES"
  },
  {
    "channel_id": "C001GENERA",
    "reactions": ":tea:x1",
    "reply_count": "0",
    "text": "found it in the toy bin behind Owen's trucks. leaving in 15, bag is intact.",
    "thread_ts": "0",
    "ts": "2025-12-28T22:32:42+00:00-v3",
    "user_id": "U001PERSONA"
  },
  {
    "channel_id": "C001GENERA",
    "reactions": ":tea:x1",
    "reply_count": "0",
    "text": "thank god. i'll be there by 8. do you have the intake forms for the Hendersons or is that Dani?",
    "thread_ts": "0",
    "ts": "2025-12-28T22:32:42+00:00-v4",
    "user_id": "U003THERES"
  },
  {
    "channel_id": "C001GENERA",
    "reactions": ":tea:x1",
    "reply_count": "0",
    "text": "Dani has them. also she moved the staff meeting to 3:30 today, heads up.",
    "thread_ts": "0",
    "ts": "2025-12-28T22:32:42+00:00-v5",
    "user_id": "U001PERSONA"
  },
  {
    "channel_id": "C001GENERA",
    "reactions": ":tea:x1",
    "reply_count": "0",
    "text": "that's my busiest prenatal block. did she send an updated invite or just... not?",
    "thread_ts": "0",
    "ts": "2025-12-28T22:32:42+00:00-v6",
    "user_id": "U003THERES"
  },
  {
    "channel_id": "C001GENERA",
    "reactions": ":tea:x1",
    "reply_count": "0",
    "text": "just texted me. very Dani. Neil's doing pickup so i can stay but you might want to loop her in directly.",
