    "ts": "2025-12-28T22:32:42+00:00-v8",
    "user_id": "U003THERES"
  },
  {
    "channel_id": "C001GENERA",
    "reactions": ":tea:x1",
    "reply_count": "0",
    "text": "Marco \u2014 where are we on the hall bathroom? My parents drive up from Hendersonville Friday and I told my mom the tile would be done. Loretta will clock the missing grout line before she even sets her bag down.",
    "thread_ts": "0",
    "ts": "2025-12-28T17:02:57+00:00",
    "user_id": "U001PERSONA"
  },
  {
    "channel_id": "C001GENERA",
    "reactions": ":tea:x1",
    "reply_count": "0",
    "text": "ha. almost there \u2014 just need to seal the floor and rehang the door. was gonna come Thursday morning if that works?",
    "thread_ts": "0",
    "ts": "2025-12-28T17:02:57+00:00-v2",
    "user_id": "U004MARCO"
  },
  {
    "channel_id": "C001GENERA",
    "reactions": ":tea:x1",
    "reply_count": "0",
    "text": "Thursday's a clinic day, I'm out by 7:15. Neil's home though. Fair warning: Owen is currently obsessed with handing strangers his shoes.",
