    "ts": "2025-12-28T17:02:57+00:00-v3",
    "user_id": "U001PERSONA"
  },
  {
    "channel_id": "C001GENERA",
    "reactions": ":tea:x1",
    "reply_count": "0",
    "text": "lol i can work with that. so Thursday 8am, should be in and out by noon, just need access to the main water shutoff",
    "thread_ts": "0",
    "ts": "2025-12-28T17:02:57+00:00-v4",
    "user_id": "U004MARCO"
  },
  {
    "channel_id": "C001GENERA",
    "reactions": ":tea:x1",
    "reply_count": "0",
    "text": "It's the panel in the hall closet, Neil knows where it is. Can you text him direct so it doesn't fall through the cracks? He's 828-555-0174.",
