    "ts": "2025-12-28T17:02:57+00:00-v5",
    "user_id": "U001PERSONA"
  },
  {
    "channel_id": "C001GENERA",
    "reactions": ":tea:x1",
    "reply_count": "0",
    "text": "got it, texting him now. anything else on the punch list while i'm there? saw that the exhaust fan was loose last time",
    "thread_ts": "0",
    "ts": "2025-12-28T17:02:57+00:00-v6",
    "user_id": "U004MARCO"
  },
  {
    "channel_id": "C001GENERA",
    "reactions": ":tea:x1",
    "reply_count": "0",
    "text": "Yes actually \u2014 fix that too. Dani came over last week and pointed it out before I did, which was embarrassing.",
