    "user_id": "U001PERSONA"
  },
  {
    "channel_id": "C001GENERA",
    "reactions": ":tea:x1",
    "reply_count": "0",
    "text": "on it. i'll have everything done before your folks show up. Loretta won't find a thing \ud83d\udc4d",
    "thread_ts": "0",
    "ts": "2025-12-28T17:02:57+00:00-v8",
    "user_id": "U004MARCO"
  },
  {
    "channel_id": "C001GENERA",
    "reactions": ":tea:x1",
    "reply_count": "0",
